videos.headline: Texas guard hop-steps between defenders for the layin

videos.description: Baylor's Al Freeman catches the ball and uses a mean jab step to get a Texas defender to fall before hitting a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Baylor guard's jab step gets defender to fall in win
Longhorns guard gets the steal and then the dunk on the other end

videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley scores on a putback dunk and gets a technical foul for elbowing the chest of Texas' Jarrett Allen.
videos.headline: Motley T'd up after powerful putback slam

videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley talks about his great game and how different teammates step up in different games.
videos.headline: Motley breaks down game against Texas

videos.description: Jon Sciambi and Miles Simon break down the game of Baylor's Johnathan Motley in a 74-64 victory over Texas.
videos.headline: Motley comes up big for Baylor in win
